               <p>WILLIAM ALLEN. I <rs id="t18180909-261-viclabel1442" type="occupation">keep the <placeName id="t18180909-261-crimeloc1443">Portland Arms, public-house, in Upper Berkley-street</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-crimeloc1443" type="placeName" value="Portland Arms, public-house, in Upper Berkley-street"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-crimeloc1443" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-261-off1440 t18180909-261-crimeloc1443"></join>
                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-261-victim1893 t18180909-261-viclabel1442"></join>. On the 30th of July, about a quarter before ten o'clock at night, I missed the copper boiler out of my kitchen.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-261-person1894">
                  WILLIAM 
                  RUSSELL
               <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1894" type="surname" value="RUSSELL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1894" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1894" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I was at the corner of Upper Berkley-street, about a quarter before ten o'clock at night, the prisoner passed me with a basket. I heard the alarm, and ran after him; he threw the basket down. I picked it up, and found the boiler in it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-261-person1895">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  RUSSEL
               <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1895" type="surname" value="RUSSEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1895" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-261-person1895" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I saw the prisoner come out of the prosecutor's house with the basket in his hand; I ran after him, he threw it down. I secured him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I know nothing of it.</p>
